text: Kinza Hashmi (, ), is a Pakistani television actress. She started her acting career in 2014 and appeared in several television commercials and serials. She played Rushna in Hum TV's Ishq Tamasha (2018) for which she received a nomination for Best Negative Actor at the Hum Awards. == Filmography == === Television === {| class="wikitable" |+Key | style="background:#ffc;"| | Denotes serial that has not yet been released |} {| class="wikitable" |- !
